widgets_values:
Background Element describe the BG and connect to the (text_d) input text concatenate node for manual BG for Auto just leave the connection on Blip Caption 

You can add something on the Difficult Concept Box to force it's generation. 

The Danbooru Caption box has a place where you can add a negative concept if is coming too strong on the show text. 

SDXL prompt styler works with 1.x too so you can use the style you like

nodes.title: TURBO SDXL PIPELINES
widgets_values:
This workflow is meant for 1.5 LCM you might be able to make it work for on XL pipeline too but you need to change models and some of the settings. 

If you want to try SDXL or Turbo don't forget to change all the models to XL and I recommend using CN models with its respective preprocessor. 

I don't think tile control lite is supported yet on CN Adv Sadly. Which is why I use 1.5 here. Delete it or switch for another option for SDXL
